Author: dawie
Title: The Difference Between Marketing, PR, Advertising, and Branding

Author: ks
Content: I think they are mostly the same, but that "developer" means more than just programming. By developing something you take an active part and can make decisions about the software. If you're "just" a programmer, you just program something that matches the specs. (think outsourcing)
